{title: Markup with Chords}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[Am]Hello <b>bold</b> world and [G]goodbye <i>italic</i> moon
[F]<b>Bold [C]with chord inside</b> the markup
[Dm]Chord then <b>[G]bold with chord</b> then normal
[Am]<i>Italic [Em]with [Am]multiple chords</i> inside
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[F]<b>[C]Bold</b> start with [G]chord and <i>[Am]italic</i> end
[F]<b>Bold</b>[C] chord right [G]after <i>italic [Am]end</i>
{end_of_chorus}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[G]<span foreground="red">[C]Red text with chords [D]inside span</span>
[Em]Normal [C]text with <highlight>[G]highlighted chord</highlight> text
{end_of_verse}
